# Strict Typing (Hard Rule)

- No `any`. No `unknown`; use concrete types or unions/branded types.
- Every function: explicit param and return types. Reuse types from `lib/types.ts`. No escape hatches (fix the type, don’t widen). `strict: true` in tsconfig; no loose generics or inline `object`.

```ts
// ✅ parse(data: string): ParsedSession   ❌ parse(data: any): unknown
```
